NAME
    Log::ger::Format::Sprintfn - Use Text::sprintfn for formatting instead
    of sprintf

VERSION
    version 0.003

SYNOPSIS
     use Log::ger::Format 'Sprintfn';
     use Log::ger;

    After that:

     log_debug 'user is %(username)s, details are %(detail)s',
         {username=>"Foo", detail=>{...}};

    Note that this only has effect in the importing package.

DESCRIPTION
SEE ALSO
    Log::ger

    Text::sprintfn

